# Project Context

## Database: Supabase PostgreSQL

### Schema Overview
- recipes (main table)
- ingredients, instructions, nutrition (related data)
- *_translations tables (i18n support for ES/EN)

### Key Files
- `supabase/schema.sql` - Complete database schema
- `src/lib/supabase.ts` - Database client
- `src/services/recipeService.ts` - CRUD operations
- `.env.local` - NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY

### Data Flow
1. AI generates recipes â†’ saves to Supabase
2. App loads recipes from Supabase (with caching)
3. Translations loaded based on locale (en/es)

### TypeScript Types
All database operations are strongly typed. See RecipeService for interfaces.

